title: MUSAA 5080 Portfolio
text:
This portfolio documents my learning journey in Public Policy Analytics (MUSA 5080).


This Course it little bit tricky because it composes on programming techniques specially the R expertise and a bulk of knowledge to the associated plugins




Weekly Notes: My learning reflections and key concepts
Labs: Completed assignments and analyses
Final Project: Capstone modeling challenge




I am at Upenn to burn midnight oil in research after gaining almost 14 years of extensive field experience in town planning and policy formulation at a key government level. I aim to pursue a Doctor of Philosophy degree in my field and conduct practical research for personal development as well as for the betterment of my profession.




Email: [umsaad@upenn.edujj]
GitHub: [https://github.com/umairbinsaad/shahrukh-khan]
